{"article_id":"SbKCWYm8lYZRayKu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Both the president and his former attorney and fixer Michael Cohen say","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"they do n't intend to enforce the hush agreement","depth":8},{"id":2,"text":"Stormy Daniels signed","depth":8},{"id":3,"text":"to stay quiet about her claims of an affair with President Donald Trump .","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"The shell company","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"Cohen used","depth":9},{"id":6,"text":"to pay Daniels","depth":9},{"id":7,"text":"agreed to throw out its hush-money agreement with the adult film star ,","depth":7},{"id":8,"text":"a lawyer for Essential Consultants said in a Friday court filing .","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Lawyers for Trump followed soon after with a filing of their own Saturday ,","depth":5},{"id":10,"text":"explaining","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"they had no intention","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"of enforcing the agreement ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"which the president never signed .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Cohen 's company asked Daniels ' to give back the $ 130,000","depth":6},{"id":15,"text":"she was paid","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"to stay silent about the alleged affair","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"she claims to have had with Trump in 2006 .","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"The president denies the affair .","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"In his letter to Daniels ' attorney Michael Avenatti , Cohen 's lawyer Brent Blakely said","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"that his client 's company `` agrees to accept the rescission of the Confidential Settlement Agreement ''","depth":7},{"id":21,"text":"and `` demands","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"that the full consideration","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"paid to Plaintiff ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"$ 130,000.00 , be returned . ''","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Avenatti pushed back after the filing Friday ,","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"that he doesn ' t have to accept the offer","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"and that he and Daniels `` will never settle the cases","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"absent full disclosure and accountability . ''","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"In an interview with CNN , Avenatti called it a `` Hail Mary ''","depth":9},{"id":31,"text":"to try to avoid Trump and Cohen facing deposition .","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"`` Michael Cohen is back to playing games","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"and trying to protect Donald Trump .","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"He is now pulling a legal stunt","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"to try and \" fix it \"","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"so that we can ' t depose Trump , ''","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"he wrote on Twitter .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"After Trump 's move , Avenatti claimed","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"the president was `` frightened '' of the possibility","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"of being deposed .","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"`` He is desperate","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"and doing all","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"he can","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"to avoid having to answer my questions , ''","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"Avenatti said on Twitter .","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Daniels ,","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"whose legal name is Stephanie Clifford ,","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"has previously offered to pay back the money","depth":6},{"id":49,"text":"in order to be freed from her non-disclosure agreement .","depth":5},{"id":50,"text":"She has also claimed","depth":5},{"id":51,"text":"that the agreement was invalid","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"because Trump never signed it .","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Friday 's filing comes amid the ongoing legal battler over the hush money","depth":5},{"id":54,"text":"paid to Daniels just days before the 2016 presidential election .","depth":5},{"id":55,"text":"Daniels is suing","depth":6},{"id":56,"text":"to void her non-disclosure agreement","depth":6},{"id":57,"text":"and alleges","depth":6},{"id":58,"text":"that Trump defamed her","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"by questioning her account of their relationship .","depth":7},{"id":60,"text":"Cohen , Trump 's former personal attorney , pleaded guilty last month to eight charges","depth":3},{"id":61,"text":"related to fraud and campaign finance violations .","depth":3},{"id":62,"text":"In his plea , Cohen said","depth":4},{"id":63,"text":"he paid off two women at Trump ' s `` direction ''","depth":5},{"id":64,"text":"to silence them before the election","depth":5},{"id":65,"text":"and admitted","depth":4},{"id":66,"text":"that the payments were illegal .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":133,"left":126,"right":132,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":112,"right":125,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":112,"left":80,"right":111,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":80,"left":75,"right":79,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":75,"left":70,"right":74,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":0,"right":69,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":69,"left":68,"right":3,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":73,"right":8,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":73,"left":72,"right":7,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":72,"left":4,"right":71,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":71,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":79,"left":9,"right":78,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":78,"left":10,"right":77,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":77,"left":11,"right":76,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":76,"left":12,"right":13,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":111,"left":84,"right":110,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":84,"left":83,"right":18,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent